IP geolocation helps to obtain information regarding a target such as its country, region/state, city, latitude and longitude of its city, ZIP/postal code, time zone, connection speed.

-> website:- https://www.ip2location.com

-> Using IP geolocation, an attacker may attempt to gather more information about a target with the help of social engineering, and non-technical attacks such as dumpster diving, as a technical expert

-> IP2Location tool to identify a visitor's geographical location, i.e., country, region, city, latitude and longitude of city, ZIP code, time zone, connection speed, ISP, domain name, IDD country code, area code

-> using this tool atacker can get the evert single detail of the visitor

-> Inofrmation like country,ISP, Domain, Mobile Network Code, etc much more.

-> also user can get tbe IP address of the visitor and can use proxies as well 
